          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Opioid Preventing Abuse through Continuing Education Act of 2017 or the Opioid PACE Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Controlled Substances Act to require a practitioner (other than a hospital, pharmacy, pharmacist, or veterinarian) to comply with a training requirement, as a condition of obtaining or renewing a registration to prescribe or dispense opioids for the treatment of pain or pain management.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
